subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Notre Dame’s win in five overtimes over Louisville was full of unusual events, including 158 shots attempted and a critical 12 points in 47 seconds by the Irish’s Jerian Grant, who had not hit a field goal until then.
